    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it still has that 'new car' magic. No scratches, no dents, and the interior is spotless. It drives like a total dream and I\u2019m only letting it go because I\u2019m downsizing. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly loved, this is the one! Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
