      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2008 BMW M3 (E92) in pristine condition. This specimen features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering 414 hp through eight individual throttle bodies and a precision 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a limited-slip M-differential, ensuring superlative lateral dynamics. Meticulously maintained with documented rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The factory-original Alpine White finish remains flawless, complemented by an unblemished Novillo leather interior. No subframe fatigue or VANOS issues. This is a turn-key, high-revving masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
